ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: perception
ⲃⲉⲣⲥⲓⲟⲛ: "1.0.0"
ⲗⲁⲛⲅⲩⲁⲅⲉ: zig
ⲙⲟⲇⲩⲗⲉ: perception

ⲥⲣⲉⲁⲧⲓⲟⲛ_ⲡⲁⲧⲧⲉⲣⲛ:
  ⲥⲟⲩⲣⲥⲉ: RawSensoryInput
  ⲧⲣⲁⲛⲥⲫⲟⲣⲙⲉⲣ: SensoryProcessing
  ⲣⲉⲥⲩⲗⲧ: ProcessedPerception

ⲃⲉⲏⲁⲃⲓⲟⲣⲥ:
  - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: process_visual
    ⲅⲓⲃⲉⲛ: Raw visual data
    ⲱⲏⲉⲛ: Apply computer vision algorithms
    ⲧⲏⲉⲛ: Return object recognition and scene understanding
    ⲧⲉⲥⲧ_ⲥⲁⲥⲉⲥ:
      - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: basic_object_detection
        ⲓⲛⲡⲩⲧ: {data: "image_bytes", format: "jpeg"}
        ⲉⲝⲡⲉⲥⲧⲉⲇ: {objects: ["person", "chair"], confidence: 0.85}

  - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: process_audio
    ⲅⲓⲃⲉⲛ: Raw audio stream
    ⲱⲏⲉⲛ: Apply speech recognition and sound analysis
    ⲧⲏⲉⲛ: Return transcribed text and sound classification
    ⲧⲉⲥⲧ_ⲥⲁⲥⲉⲥ:
      - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: speech_to_text
        ⲓⲛⲡⲩⲧ: {audio: "speech_wav", language: "en"}
        ⲉⲝⲡⲉⲥⲧⲉⲇ: {text: "Hello world", confidence: 0.92}

  - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: integrate_multimodal
    ⲅⲓⲃⲉⲛ: Multiple sensory inputs
    ⲱⲏⲉⲛ: Fuse different modalities
    ⲧⲏⲉⲛ: Return unified perception
    ⲧⲉⲥⲧ_ⲥⲁⲥⲉⲥ:
      - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: audio_visual_fusion
        ⲓⲛⲡⲩⲧ: {visual: "scene_data", audio: "speech_data"}
        ⲉⲝⲡⲉⲥⲧⲉⲇ: {integrated: "person_speaking", context: "meeting"}